'''Tagge Industries Shipyards Limited''' was a subsidiary of [[Tagge Company/Legends|Tagge Company]] that specialized in the production of [[Starship/Legends|starships]]. The company was responsible for the creation and distribution of the the [[Modular taskforce cruiser]] into the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]].

